 Set these in your Xcode scheme (Product > Scheme > Edit Scheme > Run > Arguments > Environment Variables):
 - GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_key_here
 - STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_your_key_here
 
 ### Method 2: Secrets.plist (Local Development)
 1. Copy Secrets.plist.example to Secrets.plist
 2. Fill in your API keys
 3. Secrets.plist is in .gitignore and will NOT be committed
 
 ### Method 3: On-Device Setup Screen
 If no keys are found, the app shows a setup screen where you can enter keys.
 Keys are stored in the iOS Keychain and persist across app launches.
 
 ## For Investor Demos
 Use Method 3: Simply launch the app and enter the test keys on the setup screen.
 Keys persist in the Keychain so you only need to enter them once per device.
 
 ## IMPORTANT
